      <h2>Membership Requirements</h2>
    </div>
    <p>The Boston (MA) Alumni Chapter accepts applications for membership from qualified men who meet the following criteria:</p>

    <h3 style="margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);">Undergraduate Membership</h3>
    <p>Undergraduate membership is available through our advised undergraduate chapters:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);">
      <li><strong>Chi Chapter</strong> - Boston University</li>
      <li><strong>Theta Iota Chapter</strong> - Massachusetts Institute of Technology</li>
      <li><strong>Lambda Xi Chapter</strong> - Brown University</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Contact the respective chapter's undergraduate advisor for more information.</p>

    <h3 style="margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);">Alumni Membership</h3>
    <p>Alumni membership through the Boston (MA) Alumni Chapter is available to men who:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);">
      <li>Are at least 21 years of age</li>
      <li>Have earned a minimum of a bachelor's degree from an accredited four-year college or university</li>
      <li>Demonstrate good moral character</li>
      <li>Express a genuine interest in the ideals of Kappa Alpha Psi</li>
      <li>Reside in the Greater Boston area</li>
    </ul>
